  <brief_title>Analysis of Postoperative Bandage Use Protocols in Otoplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analysis of the Influence of Different Protocols of Postoperative Elastic Bandage Use in the Results of Otoplasty</official_title>
  <sponsors>
